RE CommodityLogic NDAWe are considering them to redesign our web site Both The Adcetera Group and Organic Inc are submitting proposals to work on the project and we need them to be under the same NDA It would be great if you could email the agreement Pagogh Cho is our main contact and can distribute the agreements to the other people on the list His email address is Thanks for your help Jennifer Original Message From Jones Tana Sent Wednesday October AM To Smith Jennifer Marie Subject RE CommodityLogic NDA What is the nature of the business you are discussing Also do you want me to send this by email If so I will need thir email address Original Message From Smith Jennifer Marie Sent Wednesday October AM To Jones Tana Cc Greenberg Mark Subject CommodityLogic NDA Tana Please prepare a CommodityLogic nondisclosure agreement for The Adcetera Group similar to the NDA created for Organic Inc Here is the contact information Pagogh Cho Director Web Strategy and Development Linda Wood Marisa Walker John Sexton Kristy Sexton Address The Adcetera Group Allen Parkway Suite Houston TX fax Id like for them to receive the agreement by the end of the day if possible Please call me if you have any questions Thanks Jennifer Smith x
